    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">Index XXXIII.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXXII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXXII. de expeditione <app>
                                <rdg wit="#S1 #S3">Matthiae</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#S2">Mathiae</rdg>
                            </app> regis contra <app>
                                <lem wit="#S1">Transsilvanos</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#S2 #S3">Transilvanos</rdg>
                            </app></rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Anno, qui insecutus est, Bohemum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">quendam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">quemdam</rdg>
                    </app> Suillam nomine, qui coacta magna praedonum manu res novas moliri parabat
                    in Hungaria, in oppido, cuius nomen est <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Coztolian</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Costolia</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Coztoliam</rdg>
                    </app>, circumsessum ac debellatum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1 #L2">caepit</rdg>
                    </app>, deque eo atque illis, qui cum eo capti sunt, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R">sumpsit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sumsit</rdg>
                    </app> supplicium.</s>
                <s n="2"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1">Post haec</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #S3 #M">Posthac</rdg>
                    </app> vertit in fugam exercitum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S2 #S3">Transilvanorum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2 #M">Transylvanorum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Transsylvanorum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Transsilvanorum</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="3">Hi populi, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quamquam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">quanquam</rdg>
                    </app> tenent portionem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">quandam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">quamdam</rdg>
                    </app> Magnae Germaniae, ideoque magna ex parte lingua loquuntur Germanorum,
                    Hungarorum tamen regibus a multis iam annis antea paruerant.</s>
                <s n="4"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> in regni <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2 #S2 #M">Mathiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mathie</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S3">Matthiae</rdg>
                    </app> initiis constituto sibi principe, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">illis <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">praeesset</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">preesset</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#M">praesset</rdg>
                            </app></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">praeesset illis</rdg>
                    </app>, rebellavere.</s>
                <s n="5">Adnisi autem sunt ante omnia impedire aditus regionis, ne videlicet in
                    ipsam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S2 #S3">Transilvaniam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2 #M">Transylvaniam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Transsylvaniam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Transsilvaniam</rdg>
                    </app> copiae regiae ingrederentur, non enim facilis est ad <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">illam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">ipsam</rdg>
                    </app> accessus, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">silvae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">silve</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">sylvae</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> multis in locis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">densissimae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">densissime</rdg>
                    </app>, in aliis autem asperae alpes reddunt regionem omni ex parte aditu <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">difficillimam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1">difficilimam</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="6">At vero urgente rege <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">Hungarae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">Hungaricae</rdg>
                    </app> copiae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">(vi strenue facta)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">vi strenue facta</rdg>
                    </app> irrumpunt, viaque patefacta <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S2 #S3">Transilvanis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2 #M">Transylvanis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Transsylvanis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Transsilvanis</rdg>
                    </app> invitis multisque illorum interfectis penetrant circumquaque loca omnia,
                    tandemque in eam provinciam perveniunt.</s>
                <s n="7">Illi, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">quom</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum</rdg>
                    </app> primum regem equo armisque insignem iam introgressum conspiciunt, veluti
                    viso fulmine vertuntur in fugam, insecuti regii illos profligant, multi illorum
                    vulnerati multique interfecti, qui vero in urbibus sese continuerant, audita
                    victoria nihil morati deditionem faciunt.</s>
                <s n="8"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Plebibus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Plaebibus</rdg>
                    </app> venia a rege data, illis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">autem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">aurem</rdg>
                    </app>, qui populis persuaserant defectionem, parum profuit suae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">poenituisse</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">paenituisse</rdg>
                    </app> infidelitatis, fuerunt enim suis et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">privati</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">privatis</rdg>
                    </app> honoribus et spoliati dominatibus.</s>
                <s n="9">Est <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S2 #S3">Transilvania</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2 #M">Transylvania</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Transsylvania</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Transsilvania</rdg>
                    </app> ferax omnis generis frugum, vini laudatissimi, multorum generum fructuum
                    optimorum, qualia sunt pruna, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> vocant Damascena, mala, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cerasa</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">ceresa</rdg>
                    </app> et pira, quorum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">pleraque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">plaeraque</rdg>
                    </app> eximiae sunt magnitudinis, fert linum, crocum, equos et abunde et
                    optimos, abundat et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">aliis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">alius</rdg>
                    </app> et quidem multiplicis generis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">pecoribus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">pecoris</rdg>
                    </app> propter et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK">caeli</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">celi</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">coeli</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">clementiam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">cloementiam</rdg>
                    </app> et pascua laetissima.</s>
                <s n="10"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Fodinae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Fodine</rdg>
                    </app> in ea sunt auri, argenti, aeris, ferri, salis, plumbi, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #M">lapidicinae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">lapidicine</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">lapicidinae</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">multae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">multe</rdg>
                    </app>, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">albi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">alibi</rdg>
                    </app> praesertim rubrique marmoris, gignit alabastrum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cristallumque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">cristallum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">imprimis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">inprimis</rdg>
                    </app> laudatum.</s>
                <s n="11">Hominum ingenia magna excellentiaque, ad ea praesertim aptissima maximeque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">versatilia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">versabilia</rdg>
                    </app>, quae manu fiunt, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">pleraque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">plaeraque</rdg>
                    </app> hominum corpora procera sunt statura.</s>
                <s n="12">Multae in ea <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">pulcherrimae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">pulcherime</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">pulcherimae</rdg>
                    </app> urbes.</s>
                <s n="13">Brevibus multa complectar, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B">quitquid</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2">quicquid</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quidquid</rdg>
                    </app> est in regno Hungariae laude dignum atque excellens, quod attineat ad
                    nobiles et honorata appellatione opifices atque ad eas artes, quas appellant
                    mechanicas, id totum apud <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #S2 #S3">Transilvanos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #L2 #M">Transylvanos</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Transsylvanos</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Transsilvanos</rdg>
                    </app> habetur.</s>
                <s n="14">Testificari id equidem possum et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S3 #M">ceteri</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2">caeteri</rdg>
                    </app>, qui viderunt videntesque mire obstupuerunt.<note type="critic"
                        corresp="RKK">14 <hi rend="italic">Testificari id equidem possum et ceteri,
                            qui viderunt</hi> – ergo Ransanus iter in Transsylvaniam fecit, sicut et
                        Index II.116 demonstrat, ubi ex capitibus draconum ibi effossis unum ei dono
                        datum esse dicitur. Nota, quod Bongarsius anno 1585 ossa gigantum capitaque
                        draconum in urbe Egidiopoli Transsylvaniae (Nagyenyed) vidit. (V. Géza
                        Birkás: <title>Francia utazók Magyarországon</title>. Szeged 1948.
                        35.)</note></s>
            </p>
